{"tid":2346562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐警保皇黨2議員　獲任監警會副主席","createTime":"2020-12-30T10:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T18:02:18.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2f32c35cde0baa4cf5698849b0e86dbcd0fb0fe6","tid":2346562,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PdQEnCx_Jw7GTE90fwYWya5IIzI=/1440x810/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JQHCV5KVHRHTTMGQJKCRNY3ZAA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPdQEnCx_Jw7GTE90fwYWya5IIzI%3D%2F1440x810%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJQHCV5KVHRHTTMGQJKCRNY3ZAA.png&h=d401e49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府今日再委任多名監警會的新成員，其中兩個新副主席由工業界立法會議員吳永嘉，以及金融界立法會議員陳振英擔任，均為資深建制派。<br />\n...<br />\n高等法院上月就一宗司法覆核案，裁定現時由監警會及投訴警察課組成的兩層投訴機制，無法有效處理針對警察之投訴。惟冠以「獨立」之名的監警會，今日再獲政府委任多名新成員，其中兩個新副主席之位，由工業界立法會議員吳永嘉，以及金融界立法會議員陳振英擔任，兩人均為資深建制派，在去年反修例運動中曾公開「撐警」；連同獲再度委任的航運交通界立法會議員易志明，監警會共3名副主席，再次全數由建制派擔任。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/OEK2YQY3UVFOTE62EY7JEBDNAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FOEK2YQY3UVFOTE62EY7JEBDNAY%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=0d513888\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FOEK2YQY3UVFOTE62EY7JEBDNAY%2F&h=b85fa5df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/OEK2YQY3UVFOTE62EY7JEBDNAY/</a>"},{"pid":"6048c0f5cd50a547fb406b702922899d8de17aee","tid":2346562,"uid":167933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"d805dbcace6652df93632657375943ae5ced9d5e","tid":2346562,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:49:13.000Z",